items.badge_description: It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That’s 170 check-ins with a photo.

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 100 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 21!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 230 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 47!

While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly what’s on tap! That's 300 check-ins at venue that is verified.  Try 5 more for Level 61!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 410 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower.
Light and crisp, a Pilsner is all you need to make your day great. Though, perhaps another one would make it even better. That’s 35 different Pilsners. Try 5 more to unlock Level 8.
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 485 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 98!

user.bio: Alone in quiet places with a bottle and a song
Beer, whiskey and coffee are my loves! I use the uni scoring system for my ratings, and love both strong and light beers
Work less, play more, drink better beer
"... At least I'm holding a beer, what are you holding, dumb f-ck?" - Michael Bisping
